\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{\gamma}$
\end_inset

 (at time 
\begin_inset Formula $t=0$
\end_inset

) and change rate 
\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset

 which determines if noise increases (
\begin_inset Formula $g>1$
\end_inset

) or decreases (
\begin_inset Formula $g<1$
\end_inset

) in time as:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
V\left(\gamma\left(t\right)\right)=\sigma_{\gamma}^{2}\cdot g^{-t}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

